{"title":"共产党象太阳——福建省福安县范坑大队庆祝“七一”山歌连唱","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":11,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党象太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——福建省福安县范坑大队庆祝“七一”山歌连唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社社长陈阿兴唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党是春风吹嫩芽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万紫千红放百花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天台上新歌手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全是我社种田家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老社员陈长明接唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种田家，显才华，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全靠党的功劳大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教我田里夺丰收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教我思想革命化。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员陈阿木接唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命化，笑哈哈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主席著作一刻不离它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚刚上过几堂课，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脑子开窗亮花花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青年社员陈石妹接唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮花花，记党话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天不怕来地不怕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荒山野岭随我劈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无价宝藏任我挖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女干部吴莲萱接唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任我挖，任我画，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷白山区来绿化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南山北山榛连榛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东坡西坡茶接茶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采茶女陈琴容接唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茶接茶，美如画，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘上岭忙采茶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"片片茶叶片片情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"片片情意献国家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产队长陈冬发接唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献国家，谁不夸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"集体生产威力大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"低产从此变高产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高产再把稳产拿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧童陈安赐接唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稳产拿，顶呱呱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是队里放牛娃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"养好牛羊为革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸前也挂光荣花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知识青年陈义生接唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光荣花，珍惜它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立志农村把根扎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗红心交给党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿为革命当“傻瓜”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大队长陈国瑞接唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当“傻瓜”，非傻瓜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听话要听党的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党叫我当实干家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能带领好兵马。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民兵陈松青接唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好兵马，我参加，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永世不忘旧伤疤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台湾尚有恶狼卧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"内部敌人细清查。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老革命王冬友接唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细清查，细思想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈士鲜血换天下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧抓印把和枪杆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲碎鬼怪青獠牙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员陈福伦接唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青獠牙，敲碎它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民江山钢铁打，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三面红旗来指引，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳关大道大步跨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女林宜姿接唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大步跨，无牵挂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方放出红彩霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一轮红日高空照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光芒照耀亿万家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干部林长兴接唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亿万家，显才华，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席胜过亲爹妈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门上招招手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山区开放幸福花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党支书陈细现接唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福花，革命花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开遍海角与天涯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界人民暖洋洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京太阳放光华。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老贫农陈品珍接唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放光华，真不差，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席象中堂挂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天抬头望一望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年岁少了一大把。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员陈祥发接唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一大把，把油加，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天地山河起变化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产主义新天堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我手中露萌芽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团干部陈发松唱尾声："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"露萌芽，催发葩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山歌还有十万八，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是社员土特产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不嫌粗陋党收下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔陈发松整理〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}